name: File Covers for Figma
description:
A small file covers kit with several styles and unique waves-like artwork for each color.


A kit includes:

  • 3 styles for each cover (Dark, Light, Alternative)
  • 8 colors for each style (Blue, Red, Green, Purple, Pink, Yellow, Teal, Sunset) with unique SVG shapes.


Artworks created by Haikei.app generators.
